data.description: POOL HOME!! No HOA! Priced below market! Nestled away in a highly desirable Deltona Lakes community is your home sweet home! Sits on an expansive 0.37 Acre lot, you can enjoy all the privacy & serenity this home has to offer as it is surrounded by lush landscaping creating a tropical park-like setting. Nicely renovated inside and out into a stunning new looking home. The contemporary feel continues inside as you discover a fully updated interior with an open floor plan layout seamlessly connecting the main living areas for easy living & great entertaining. The living and dining rooms overlook the fully modernized kitchen with gas available. Simply stunning, it is equipped with new top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, designer fixtures and gleaming dark quartz counter tops that dramatically contrast the classic cabinetry. The over sized center kitchen island is a chef's dream, & doubles as a breakfast bar for casual dining. Just off the kitchen the pool/fun!
